Utility function to make a dataframe from the IRTmodel

prepare_for_plots.Rd

This is a utility function to make a dataframe from the IRTmodel, which makes it easier to plot trace lines

prepare_for_plots(mod)

Arguments

mod

IRT model, either from function irtmodel or the R package mirt.

Value

Dataframe with output probabilities from the IRT model for all algorithms.

Examples

data(classification)
mod <- irtmodel(classification)
